com.ge.predix.solsvc.websocket.config

Class DefaultWebSocketConfigForTimeseries

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ge.predix.solsvc.restclient.config.DefaultOauthRestConfig
      • com.ge.predix.solsvc.websocket.config.DefaultWebSocketConfigForTimeseries
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.ge.predix.solsvc.restclient.config.IOauthRestConfig, IWebSocketConfig, org.springframework.beans.factory.Aware, org.springframework.context.EnvironmentAware

    @Component(value="defaultWebSocketConfig")
public class DefaultWebSocketConfigForTimeseries
extends com.ge.predix.solsvc.restclient.config.DefaultOauthRestConfig
implements IWebSocketConfig, org.springframework.context.EnvironmentAware
    This default WebSocket Config is tailored to Predix Timeseries properties. If you need to define another WebSocket endpoint, such as to a custom WebSocket Server, simply implement the interface and override this default properties in the WebSocket Factory.
    Author:
    212438846 Class WebSocketConfig implements IWebSocketConfig. Every separate websocket server connection requires the IWebSocketConfig interface to be implemented per connection.
